oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The synthesis and characterization of the first examples of two tellurium compounds based on 2-phenyl-5,6-dihydro-4H-1,3-oxazine substrate are described. Intramolecular (TeN)-N-... interaction in [2-(2-phenyl-5,6-dihydro-4H-1,3-oxazinyl)] tellurenyl chloride is established by single X-ray crystallography. (c) 2005
